854
01:44:07,251 --> 01:44:11,881
No thanks. I don't drink.
I don't want it

855
01:44:12,156 --> 01:44:17,890
Drink it up... listen to me.
Just a little... come on

856
01:44:24,902 --> 01:44:26,233
