863
01:45:18,956 --> 01:45:23,290
Everyone wants a slender waist

864
01:45:36,374 --> 01:45:42,973
If only your heart
could win over the waist

865
01:45:57,995 --> 01:45:59,986
Fun, wasn't it?

866
01:46:00,398 --> 01:46:05,734
The song's over, so is the booze

867
01:46:12,009 --> 01:46:14,000
You have a smoke...

868
01:46:18,649 --> 01:46:20,810
I'll get lots of booze

869
01:46:32,029 --> 01:46:40,027
When you drop ash in this ashtray
you must know it's not the ashtray...

870
01:46:41,439 --> 01:46:43,839
but me it's falling on.
- Oh yes!

871
01:47:00,057 --> 01:47:04,050
What are you staring at?
This way

872
01:47:07,398 --> 01:47:10,060
This way... look here

873
01:47:13,070 --> 01:47:14,867
What?

874
01:47:16,374 --> 01:47:20,868
What are you staring at
with your big...

875
01:47:24,248 --> 01:47:29,481
no, with your two small eyes.
What are you looking at?

876
01:47:51,175 --> 01:47:55,111
All I did was to look
at this little waist

877
01:47:56,614 --> 01:48:01,108
Who do you think you are?
You're very beautiful?

878
01:48:02,286 --> 01:48:07,451
Your face is like a chameleon's,
a pencil-thin nose...

879
01:48:10,194 --> 01:48:13,129
and your body?
It's all right

880
01:48:14,698 --> 01:48:18,134
Your waist is the only thing
one can look at

881
01:48:18,636 --> 01:48:20,627
This little waist

882
01:48:23,140 --> 01:48:28,134
Draped in a black sari,
that little area...

883
01:48:28,579 --> 01:48:34,677
is like a lemon.
No, lemons are yellow

884
01:48:37,154 --> 01:48:41,818
In reds and yellows, if it's shown up
in a romantic light...

885
01:48:42,059 --> 01:48:45,153
naturally, I will look at it.
If you mind...

886
01:48:45,362 --> 01:48:47,694
you mustn't show it at all

887
01:48:49,567 --> 01:48:53,765
Just as your face is a part
of your body, so is your waist

888
01:48:54,171 --> 01:48:57,971
I look at your face, you don't mind.
I see the waist, you mind. What for?

889
01:48:58,509 --> 01:49:00,909
Tell me, darling. Speak

890
01:49:02,646 --> 01:49:06,776
Not just your body, I'm going to
take a look at your whole body now

891
01:49:12,690 --> 01:49:15,750
You have no right to
stand there before me!

892
01:50:17,588 --> 01:50:19,579
You have no right to touch it!

893
01:50:35,406 --> 01:50:37,738
I came here to discuss
something important with you

894
01:50:38,175 --> 01:50:41,269
But neither are you in the mood to
listen, nor am I in the mood to tell

895
01:50:50,621 --> 01:50:54,853
Khushi, I've done nothing.
It's my Bengali friend

896
01:50:55,292 --> 01:50:57,283
