897
01:50:59,396 --> 01:51:03,093
If people smoke and drink,
why must I care?

898
01:51:03,767 --> 01:51:07,635
It isn't necessary for me
to know why you had liquor

899
01:51:28,325 --> 01:51:29,656
Want some?

900
01:51:32,496 --> 01:51:35,829
I came here because I thought
you were a nice human being

901
01:51:36,333 --> 01:51:39,131
But you're worse than
I could ever imagine

902
01:51:44,341 --> 01:51:46,002
If you'd listen...

903
01:52:32,556 --> 01:52:35,889
You're a performer...

904
01:52:36,593 --> 01:52:39,391
you can't make me dance

905
01:52:40,497 --> 01:52:43,898
