and pinched it

911
01:53:07,491 --> 01:53:11,757
But this is a three-year old tune.
- What a thief!

912
01:53:12,429 --> 01:53:17,093
I composed the tune three days ago,
and he stole it three years back!

913
01:53:17,835 --> 01:53:19,700
No more qawwali for me!

914
01:53:32,850 --> 01:53:35,182
How did you know it's Priya
without even looking at her?

915
01:53:35,719 --> 01:53:40,850
The fragrance! I can tell every
beautiful girl from her fragrance

916
01:53:42,459 --> 01:53:44,791
Where's this stink coming from?
Lay off!

917
01:53:51,535 --> 01:53:54,265
You like my wig, don't you?
Here you are

918
01:54:04,648 --> 01:54:08,482
Remember, the cultural programme at
the college is fast approaching?

919
01:54:09,920 --> 01:54:13,083
Join Karan immediately
and start your rehearsals

920
01:54:13,957 --> 01:54:15,618
No, Master.
- Why?

921
01:54:16,493 --> 01:54:19,087
I can't participate in this function.
- Why not?

922
01:54:19,830 --> 01:54:21,957
I've told you. I'm not participating

923
01:54:28,505 --> 01:54:34,102
Mukesh, make a team of Karan and Roma
and send them on the stage

924
01:54:34,511 --> 01:54:36,308
You have my blessings!

925
01:54:43,520 --> 01:54:47,513
Who's Roma?
- You don't know Roma? Roma!

926
01:54:47,925 --> 01:54:51,918
A new student in the first year!
She's kicked up a storm in the college

927
01:54:52,396 --> 01:54:56,924
The students are crazy about her
and go around her like blind men

928
01:54:57,334 --> 01:54:58,232
What for?

929
01:55:26,930 --> 01:55:30,229
Could you help me cross the road?
- What for?

930
01:55:30,567 --> 01:55:32,967
A blind man needs help

931
01:56:00,931 --> 01:56:03,593
You've crossed the road.
- Small road

932
01:56:03,934 --> 01:56:06,596
What?
- You've helped a blind man

933
01:56:07,004 --> 01:56:09,598
Thank you so much.
You are large-hearted

934
01:56:13,677 --> 01:56:16,009
Slipped out of my hands! Damn it!

935
01:56:28,125 --> 01:56:30,423
What is the matter?
- Priya has sent a letter

936
01:56:31,128 --> 01:56:33,119
You can give it to Vicky.
- It's not for him

937
01:56:33,297 --> 01:56:34,628
Is it for me?
- No

938
01:56:34,798 --> 01:56:36,197
It must be for you then.
- No

939
01:56:36,366 --> 01:56:38,630
If not for me, you nor Vicky...
- It's for the two of us!

940
01:56:50,981 --> 01:56:52,972
You read it

941
01:57:01,992 --> 01:57:04,256
I love Vicky so dearly...

942
01:57:04,661 --> 01:57:07,459
I don't think anyone in
the world loves anyone as much

943
01:57:08,265 --> 01:57:12,998
You must think why every lover
in the world says that

944
01:57:14,037 --> 01:57:16,471
It's because they have
true love for each other

945
01:57:17,274 --> 01:57:21,267
And the suffering of separation
those truly in love go through...

946
01:57:21,678 --> 01:57:23,475
only I know about

947
01:57:23,914 --> 01:57:28,681
I'm pining to meet Vicky.
Please bring us together

948
01:57:30,754 --> 01:57:32,483
Yours, Priya

949
01:57:33,690 --> 01:57:35,282
What are we to do now?

950
01:57:37,694 --> 01:57:40,060
Priya has a friend called
Shehnaz, right?

951
01:57:46,703 --> 01:57:48,466
How are you, Rukhsana?
- I'm fine

952
01:57:49,706 --> 01:57:51,230
Be careful, Vicky

953
01:57:55,712 --> 01:57:58,112
The two of you chat,
I'm going to bed

954
01:58:07,457 --> 01:58:09,448
Who's this girl?

955
01:58:09,726 --> 01:58:11,717
It's Shabana.
Shehnaz's friend

956
01:58:22,739 --> 01:58:25,071
Is she coming here
for the first time?

957
01:58:26,143 --> 01:58:27,132
Yes

958
01:58:28,912 --> 01:58:32,746
I see. Go ahead and
chat with Rukhsana...

959
01:58:33,550 --> 01:58:35,745
I'll take Shabana around the house

960
01:58:36,219 --> 01:58:38,210
Come on, Shabana.
- Run away, Vicky!

961
01:59:07,217 --> 01:59:09,777
Car number 906.
Is it yours?

962
01:59:10,220 --> 01:59:11,778
Yes.
- Karan?

963
02:01:57,954 --> 02:01:59,945
Let me do it

964
02:02:56,012 --> 02:02:59,004
How are you related to the girl?
- I...

965
02:03:00,483 --> 02:03:03,748
Help me with the injection.
- All right

966
02:03:17,701 --> 02:03:19,032
In the waist

967
02:03:23,039 --> 02:03:26,031
Give it to her in the arm.
- This is meant for the waist

968
02:03:26,209 --> 02:03:28,837
No, give it to her in the arm.
- The one for the arm...

969
02:03:29,112 --> 02:03:32,707
is given in the arm, the one
for the waist is given in the waist

970
02:03:35,618 --> 02:03:38,610
You don't know anything
about this waist, doctor

971
02:03:39,122 --> 02:03:43,388
This waist has caused
a very big problem already

972
02:03:44,060 --> 02:03:47,791
If I go into details,
it'll take at least 2 hours

973
02:03:48,264 --> 02:03:50,858
Your duty hours will be over
and when the next doctor comes...

974
02:03:51,201 --> 02:03:54,728
I'll have to explain to him!
Have mercy on me...

975
02:03:55,071 --> 02:03:57,062
and give it to her in the arm

976
02:04:03,079 --> 02:04:06,810
That's all right!
You can give it wherever you wish

977
02:04:07,317 --> 02:04:10,753
Give it to anyone. To her,
the nurse or yourself...

978
02:04:11,488 --> 02:04:13,888
I've seen nothing,
I will see nothing

979
02:04:15,558 --> 02:04:18,425
God, why did You make
this waist? Why?

980
02:04:46,556 --> 02:04:49,548
My heart, my love...

981
02:04:51,694 --> 02:04:54,458
I've given to you

982
02:04:56,132 --> 02:04:59,124
My love...

983
02:05:01,171 --> 02:05:04,140
what have you done?

984
02:05:05,241 --> 02:05:09,143
When our gaze met,
I realised...

985
02:05:09,846 --> 02:05:14,146
I'm crazy about you

986
02:05:14,751 --> 02:05:18,687
It's something my heart knows

987
02:05:19,956 --> 02:05:23,551
You're the one
I've taken for my beloved

988
02:06:36,232 --> 02:06:39,827
On your lips, is a smile.
Your eyes hold an intoxication

989
02:06:40,270 --> 02:06:44,229
The sight of you
makes my heart sway

990
02:06:45,542 --> 02:06:49,911
I love you all day and night.
I find peace only after meeting you

991
02:06:51,114 --> 02:06:59,044
Your dark tressses
lend a fragrance to my being

992
02:07:00,156 --> 02:07:04,593
All I wish to say is that
it's your arms I must stay in

993
02:07:05,261 --> 02:07:09,527
Don't ever forget
this promise

994
02:07:10,133 --> 02:07:14,263
Don't make me cry,
now that you make me smile

995
02:07:14,971 --> 02:07:18,873
Don't make excuses...

996
02:07:20,076 --> 02:07:23,944
don't ever hide
anything from me

997
02:07:30,887 --> 02:07:33,947
My heart, my love...

998
02:07:36,192 --> 02:07:38,956
I've given to you

999
02:08:29,145 --> 02:08:32,945
My dream, my desire...

1000
02:08:33,349 --> 02:08:37,342
is to adorn your arms
with bridal bangles

1001
02:08:38,354 --> 02:08:42,916
These lovely meetings,
I love the way you talk...

1002
02:08:43,526 --> 02:08:47,519
Should you consent, my love...

1003
02:08:47,864 --> 02:08:51,698
I'd bring the bridal palanquin
to your house

1004
02:08:53,036 --> 02:08:57,632
I spend my nights pining.
I dream of marriage

1005
02:08:58,441 --> 02:09:02,377
My world of love,
you must embellish...

1006
02:09:03,046 --> 02:09:06,709
never leave me ever

1007
02:09:08,251 --> 02:09:11,880
Keep your promises

1008
02:09:12,889 --> 02:09:16,882
Always hold me in your arms

1009
02:09:23,299 --> 02:09:26,791
My heart, my love...

1010
02:09:28,805 --> 02:09:31,399
I've given to you

1011
02:09:33,676 --> 02:09:36,406
My love...

1012
02:09:38,414 --> 02:09:41,406
what have you done?

1013
02:09:55,832 --> 02:09:57,424
What is it? What?

1014
02:09:57,600 --> 02:10:00,091
I tried several times to
meet you at your office

1015
02:10:00,436 --> 02:10:03,098
But you staff wouldn't let me.
So...

1016
02:10:04,974 --> 02:10:06,965
My name is Karan

1017
02:10:08,444 --> 02:10:11,436
Vicky's my friend, sir.
His past is nothing...

1018
02:10:12,181 --> 02:10:15,241
at present, he's a student
and he has a very bright future

1019
02:10:15,618 --> 02:10:17,449
You don't know that,
but I do

1020
02:10:17,787 --> 02:10:20,950
At my age, my father was
even worse off than Vicky is

1021
02:10:22,458 --> 02:10:25,450
At this age, even you...
don't take offense

1022
02:10:25,962 --> 02:10:28,795
You used to be a small-time thug

1023
02:10:29,532 --> 02:10:31,864
But I tell you, at your age...

1024
02:10:32,034 --> 02:10:35,470
Vicky will be far ahead of you,
me and even my father

1025
02:10:37,573 --> 02:10:40,474
Apart from all this,
he has a very kind heart

1026
02:10:43,479 --> 02:10:46,471
When a boy falls in love
with a girl...

1027
02:10:47,550 --> 02:10:50,485
and he finds the girl
without any problem...

1028
02:10:52,488 --> 02:10:57,221
imagine how happy it'll make him.
Please don't separate them

1029
02:10:57,894 --> 02:11:00,089
Please unite them

1030
02:11:08,504 --> 02:11:11,234
Your two minutes are up.
Let's go, Gotya

1031
02:11:15,311 --> 02:11:17,176
Did he have nothing to say?

1032
02:11:17,513 --> 02:11:19,913
Your two minutes are up, he said.
And left

1033
02:11:24,520 --> 02:11:27,114
All right.
Even if he said nothing...

1034
02:11:27,523 --> 02:11:30,788
couldn't you guess
what was on his mind?

1035
02:11:31,127 --> 02:11:34,528
What?
- I ask...

1036
02:11:34,797 --> 02:11:37,527
couldn't you guess
what was on his mind?

1037
02:11:39,936 --> 02:11:43,531
If one knew what's on everyone's mind,
there wouldn't be any problem at all

1038
02:11:44,040 --> 02:11:46,270
We have these problems
because we don't know

1039
02:11:46,542 --> 02:11:49,534
What do you mean by these problems?
- These problems. Period

1040
02:11:53,549 --> 02:11:55,881
All right. I must leave now

1041
02:12:10,700 --> 02:12:12,565
Did you call?

1042
02:12:13,836 --> 02:12:14,996
Yes

1043
02:12:15,238 --> 02:12:16,569
What for?

1044
02:12:18,941 --> 02:12:21,910
To talk.
- That's what we've been doing

1045
02:12:23,646 --> 02:12:26,114
No, there's something else
I want to talk about

1046
02:12:31,988 --> 02:12:34,252
What is it about?

1047
02:12:36,759 --> 02:12:41,594
She knows... why must she
ask what it's about

1048
02:12:42,732 --> 02:12:44,393
The arrogant one!

1049
02:12:49,005 --> 02:12:51,940
It's about what you think

1050
02:12:54,677 --> 02:12:58,078
I'm thinking about nothing.
You wanted to talk to me

1051
02:12:58,347 --> 02:13:00,338
So tell me what you want to

1052
02:13:19,936 --> 02:13:22,632
Is that what you called me to say?
- Yes

1053
02:14:36,712 --> 02:14:39,237
Your intoxicating eyes...

1054
02:14:42,151 --> 02:14:44,381
your lips...

1055
02:14:50,159 --> 02:14:53,151
there's a huge list
I have of you

1056
02:15:01,103 --> 02:15:04,937
Roma, can you fall in love with me?

1057
02:15:07,743 --> 02:15:09,734
Can you really like me?

1058
02:15:11,013 --> 02:15:12,742
However...

1059
02:15:14,750 --> 02:15:20,313
the possibility of me
falling in love with you...

1060
02:15:24,427 --> 02:15:27,760
does exist.
- Thanks

1061
02:15:36,772 --> 02:15:41,436
I don't you well, you see.
Let's see each other for a few days...

1062
02:15:41,777 --> 02:15:44,769
and then I'll decide about it.
It'll take a bit of time, okay?

1063
02:15:46,115 --> 02:15:50,779
What's a bit... take all the time.
All my time is now yours

1064
02:15:56,592 --> 02:16:00,119
I feel as if something is
stirred in my heart for you

1065
02:16:01,797 --> 02:16:03,594
Your lovely tresses...

1066
02:16:05,101 --> 02:16:07,092
your rose-like lips...

1067
02:16:14,210 --> 02:16:16,201
and this lovely neck and...

1068
02:16:26,822 --> 02:16:31,987
I'm not calling you because
you have a girl in your arms

1069
02:16:33,829 --> 02:16:38,391
Neither have I called you because
you're drawing pictures on her body

1070
02:16:39,502 --> 02:16:41,834
I haven't called out
to disturb you

1071
02:16:43,839 --> 02:16:47,832
We've got to be at Priya's place
at 7:30. You remember that?

1072
02:16:48,844 --> 02:16:56,512
Karan, who's she? A friend?
- A friend? Oh no, no chance at all

1073
02:16:57,653 --> 02:17:01,180
Is she a lover then?
- Lover? How disgusting!

1074
02:17:02,658 --> 02:17:06,856
To be my lover,
a girl needs extra qualities

1075
02:17:08,697 --> 02:17:10,597
So who's she?

1076
02:17:14,670 --> 02:17:19,869
She's Khushi. There's nothing else
I know about her

1077
02:17:20,876 --> 02:17:25,472
Karan, just 15 minutes to go
for 7:30. May we leave now?

1078
02:17:32,288 --> 02:17:34,620
When will you meet me again?
- Again?

1079
02:17:39,228 --> 02:17:43,562
At lunch?
- Not lunch. At dinner

1080
02:17:44,900 --> 02:17:51,237
At night. Candle-light.
Sunday 10, at my place

1081
02:18:05,020 --> 02:18:06,351
Shall we?

1082
02:18:18,434 --> 02:18:21,301
Today's Sunday.
So?

1083
02:18:54,970 --> 02:18:57,302
It was you who said it...

1084
02:18:57,973 --> 02:19:00,237
Yes, I did, but...

1085
02:20:13,048 --> 02:20:15,642
Whoever you are with,
why must I care?

1086
02:20:31,066 --> 02:20:33,057
Sorry, I'm late

1087
02:20:43,078 --> 02:20:47,845
What happened?
- Last night... nothing

1088
02:20:52,087 --> 02:20:55,887
What did Priya have to say?
- She says forget it

1089
02:20:56,925 --> 02:20:58,893
Forget what?
- Love

1090
02:20:59,161 --> 02:21:02,688
Whose love?
- The love Vicky had for Priya

1091
02:21:03,165 --> 02:21:05,099
Priya asks to forget it

1092
02:21:09,104 --> 02:21:10,901
And what did you tell her?

1093
02:21:11,106 --> 02:21:13,700
When she herself isn't interested,
what can I do?

1094
02:21:14,143 --> 02:21:18,477
What is it with girls? Flirt when you
want to, dump the guy when you wish

1095
02:21:19,348 --> 02:21:23,648
Have you girls ever considered
what it does to us guys?

1096
02:21:24,119 --> 02:21:25,916
You're acting like
a very decent guy?

1097
02:21:26,121 --> 02:21:28,521
Do you think I don't know
the truth about you?

1098
02:21:28,924 --> 02:21:31,916
Were you breathing heavily
last night, or weren't you?

1099
02:21:32,628 --> 02:21:33,390
What?

1100
02:21:34,163 --> 02:21:36,393
Were you breathing last night,
or weren't you?

1101
02:21:36,565 --> 02:21:41,468
Breathing? I was breathing last night
and the night before that too

1102
02:21:41,870 --> 02:21:45,738
And I breathe every day...
and well at that

1103
02:21:46,141 --> 02:21:48,803
It's good for the health.
Is it bad to breathe?

1104
02:21:49,144 --> 02:21:52,136
Maybe it's bad to look at this...
but why's it bad to breathe?

1105
02:21:52,681 --> 02:21:54,876
How will man live
if he doesn't breathe?

1106
02:21:55,150 --> 02:21:58,142
Am I the only one who breathes?
Everyone does. Every single day

1107
02:21:58,554 --> 02:22:01,546
Your parents do, so do mine.
Because they breathe...

1108
02:22:01,824 --> 02:22:05,487
you are here, I am here...
so's the dog

1109
02:22:06,161 --> 02:22:09,892
He breathes every day.
Nicely at that. Right puppy?

1110
02:22:11,166 --> 02:22:13,691
See? If you call that bad,
what can I do?

1111
02:22:14,636 --> 02:22:17,161
The breathing I spoke about is
different from the one you allude to

1112
02:22:17,573 --> 02:22:20,974
It's all the same. If breathing
is wrong, everything is wrong

1113
02:22:21,510 --> 02:22:23,102
I'll leave if you talk like this

1114
02:22:28,183 --> 02:22:30,981
I know the suffering of one
truly in love

1115
02:22:31,353 --> 02:22:34,845
Priya's words, weren't they?
So how can she ask us to forget it?

1116
02:22:35,190 --> 02:22:37,852
What does it mean?
We have to talk

1117
02:22:48,570 --> 02:22:52,734
Today's the last day at college.
It's time to separate

1118
02:22:53,208 --> 02:22:55,540
So come forth and take my blessings

1119
02:23:12,227 --> 02:23:13,888
You been in a crowded train?

1120
02:23:18,800 --> 02:23:21,826
So many of them have
gone into coma for you

1121
02:23:22,237 --> 02:23:27,038
I'm in a coma too. Embrace me
and revive me from the coma, Roma

1122
02:23:33,582 --> 02:23:36,050
Priya's wedding has been fixed

1123
02:23:47,262 --> 02:23:49,253
What are we to do?

1124
02:23:55,737 --> 02:23:56,726
Greetings

1125
02:23:59,608 --> 02:24:01,599
Mr Zorawar Singh... over here

1126
02:24:07,783 --> 02:24:10,274
Where are you going?
To fetch your daughter?

1127
02:24:11,286 --> 02:24:17,555
She's with us right now.
She's marrying the man she loves

1128
02:24:47,990 --> 02:24:50,982
From the look of it, it appears
as if you want to give me a thrashing

1129
02:24:53,629 --> 02:24:57,121
Don't even think of it.
Pray to God...

1130
02:24:57,933 --> 02:25:00,925
that I come to no harm.
If something happens to me...

1131
02:25:01,503 --> 02:25:04,734
you'll be the guilty one
in the eyes of the law

1132
02:25:05,474 --> 02:25:07,942
I've made arrangements, you know

1133
02:25:10,412 --> 02:25:13,347
You're picking up something
to throw at me

1134
02:25:18,820 --> 02:25:22,017
Forget me...
you can't even touch my image

1135
02:25:28,697 --> 02:25:31,757
Spend a month in Mahabaleshwar
before you return to Calcutta

1136
02:25:32,534 --> 02:25:36,026
Dad has found a job for you
over there. Okay?

1137
02:25:37,372 --> 02:25:39,772
Spend your lives together.
Be happy

1138
02:26:02,597 --> 02:26:07,796
There are problems between
you and Khushi, isn't it?

1139
02:26:10,906 --> 02:26:18,813
You know why man faces problems?
Because he hides his feelings

1140
02:26:20,215 --> 02:26:23,207
If you speak your heart,
you face no problems

1141
02:26:23,418 --> 02:26:25,409
But I don't know why man
doesn't understand that

1142
02:26:26,054 --> 02:26:28,818
He loves someone,
but he pretends to hate her

1143
02:26:29,091 --> 02:26:31,821
He hates someone and he pretends
to love her. What for?

1144
02:26:33,095 --> 02:26:38,829
Poor heart. Why do we burden
it with a thousand worries...

1145
02:26:39,434 --> 02:26:44,770
and make life unbearable for it?
If you love her...

1146
02:26:44,940 --> 02:26:47,773
tell her that you love her,
or tell her that you don't

1147
02:26:50,445 --> 02:26:53,437
God has given you eyes to see,
ears to hear...

1148
02:26:54,783 --> 02:26:58,116
and a heart to love

1149
02:27:00,122 --> 02:27:03,853
So forget about egoes
and fall in love

1150
02:27:04,459 --> 02:27:05,858
Love each other

1151
02:27:07,529 --> 02:27:11,124
I've told you how I feel

1152
02:27:36,124 --> 02:27:39,753
You've been a great help in uniting
my friend with his beloved

1153
02:27:48,003 --> 02:27:54,169
Thanks to you too. In uniting
my friend with her beloved...

1154
02:27:57,512 --> 02:28:01,915
you've been a great help.
Thank you

1155
02:30:53,688 --> 02:30:55,087
This is Seema here

1156
02:30:58,493 --> 02:31:00,688
I'm leaving today
- Okay

1157
02:31:01,196 --> 02:31:05,690
I'm leaving and you're just...
- I have another tension, Seema

1158
02:31:28,723 --> 02:31:31,055
Sir, the taxi has arrived

1159
02:31:52,747 --> 02:31:56,148
Karan?
- He has left for VT Station

1160
02:31:56,251 --> 02:31:58,549
Which train is it?
- Howrah Mail at 7:15

1161
02:32:05,160 --> 02:32:06,855
Is Khushi there?
- She has left

1162
02:32:06,928 --> 02:32:08,759
Where to?
- Bombay Central

1163
02:32:09,764 --> 02:32:12,756
Which train?
- Golden Temple Express at 7:10

1164
02:32:45,300 --> 02:32:47,598
Karan?
- No one has arrived yet

1165
02:33:33,848 --> 02:33:36,248
Was there a girl called Khushi here?
- There's no one

1166
02:34:10,518 --> 02:34:12,884
Maybe he has gone to
Mumbai Central to meet me

1167
02:34:13,888 --> 02:34:16,516
Maybe she has gone to
VT Station to meet me

1168
02:34:16,658 --> 02:34:17,886
And what if he hasn't?

1169
02:34:18,293 --> 02:34:19,282
Now?

1170
02:34:30,238 --> 02:34:35,301
A girl called Khushi will come here.
Please give her this letter

1171
02:34:37,912 --> 02:34:41,575
A boy called Karan will come here.
Please give him this

1172
02:36:26,654 --> 02:36:28,417
Karan?
- Yes?

1173
02:36:32,360 --> 02:36:36,421
I've been wanting to tell you
something for a very long time

1174
02:36:37,198 --> 02:36:40,429
You know?
I love you, Khushi

1175
02:36:43,137 --> 02:36:46,038
When we were together,
this is what I wanted to say...

1176
02:36:46,274 --> 02:36:49,835
but I never could,
I don't know why

1177
02:36:50,211 --> 02:36:53,703
And now that I want to speak,
you are not with me

1178
02:36:53,915 --> 02:36:56,850
We said so much to each other
when we fought...

1179
02:36:57,051 --> 02:37:02,455
but we couldn't say one single word
to get together. I'm sorry, Khushi

1180
02:37:04,859 --> 02:37:08,454
When I freed my hand from yours
after thanking you...

1181
02:37:08,563 --> 02:37:11,054
I felt something strange
stir in my heart

1182
02:37:11,299 --> 02:37:14,393
I don't know what it was.
But I need you, Karan

1183
02:37:16,237 --> 02:37:22,233
I now realise that the fights
we had was all part of our love

1184
02:37:24,078 --> 02:37:30,483
I need you, Khushi.
To love me, to fight with me

1185
02:37:38,693 --> 02:37:41,719
You're a lucky girl to have
found a father like yours

1186
02:37:41,896 --> 02:37:43,830
Ever since you agreed
to the wedding...

1187
02:37:43,898 --> 02:37:46,093
all he has done is to
look out for suitors

1188
02:37:46,200 --> 02:37:50,500
He decided to have Lali married
the day she returned from the city

1189
02:37:50,605 --> 02:37:53,438
Everything is ready.
The bridegroom, the garland...

1190
02:37:53,608 --> 02:37:56,509
step forward and be garlanded

1191
02:38:08,122 --> 02:38:10,113
Lali! My child!

1192
02:38:11,125 --> 02:38:13,525
You're back! Welcome!

1193
02:38:13,728 --> 02:38:16,288
Go and get ready quickly.
- But Papa...

1194
02:38:16,531 --> 02:38:20,524
Just don't worry, my little girl.
The boy I've chosen this time...

1195
02:38:21,135 --> 02:38:24,127
is neither running away
nor leaving behind letters...

1196
02:38:24,372 --> 02:38:27,136
and he's not in love with
another girl either

1197
02:38:28,276 --> 02:38:31,143
Why're you chanting Papa?
Go and get dressed quickly

1198
02:38:31,479 --> 02:38:33,140
Coming!

1199
02:38:45,827 --> 02:38:48,159
Lali, take a look
at your bridegroom

1200
02:38:49,797 --> 02:38:51,162
Take a look at him

1201
02:39:10,184 --> 02:39:12,584
You left this note for him
in the train...

1202
02:39:13,187 --> 02:39:15,178
and he turned out to be
faster than you

1203
